{
  "stem": "19130.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 410.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had-- you know, they left something there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They would, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were ourselves, before they took us in the ghetto, we hide some things, you know, in the barn.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We just hide them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, we make a hole, and we-- we covered this in the dirt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some things they find.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And some things they didn't find.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So one time, my brother-in-law, he has Christians that he used to deal with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was very, very good terms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took one, and we went back to Korost, nighttime, you know, nobody sees.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very dangerous things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came to-- and we find things, what-- what we had there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time was soap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Soap was something that you couldn't buy for money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had soap.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we-- and that Christian who hauled us in his-- and we used to-- used to sell to somebody, and for some food, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In this way, we used to-- matter things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was for a while later, my brother-in-law came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said that the Christian said that somebody steal that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How did you get out at night?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, we used to-- it was very-- the fence were very high.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you have to leave, you have to-- so we-- we put a piece of wood here, you know, you can step with the-- with a foot to jump over.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this way, we had our places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from the other side was a garden, you know, a garden.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you can hide there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We try everything just to-- just to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was some-- clothes-- you know, clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had the-- we have-- my sister was ready for marriage.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
